name: sacc
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "sacc" %}
{% set version = "0.5.2" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://github.com/LSSTDESC/sacc/archive/v{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 6da3871ca7ef38719076a683a44bc815064f209cf55c08e89e8ded0c2d569cf4

build:
  noarch: python
  number: 0
  script_env:
    - SETUPTOOLS_SCM_PRETEND_VERSION={{ version }}
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv

requirements:
  host:
    - python >=3.6
    - pip
    - setuptools_scm
  run:
    - python >=3.6
    - astropy
    - scipy
    - numpy
    - numpydoc

test:
  imports:
    - sacc

about:
  home: https://github.com/LSSTDESC/sacc
  license: BSD-3-Clause
  license_family: BSD
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: Save All Correlations and Covariances

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - beckermr
